      "title": "16 MPs write to Kota asking him to resign",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Many members of Parliament of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna have urged President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to step down.",
        "16 M.P.s of Motu Party, including Dulles, have written an urgent letter to the President, urging him to resign."
      ],
